data.description: Turn key. Rare opportunity single story home with 1,949 Sq Ft in leaving area on a 4,767 Sq Ft lot. It is nestled in the charming, desirable and quiet Cherry Cove neighborhood, north of Del Amo. This well-maintained property features an open floor plan, 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and a good-sized backyard with a new patio perfect for entertaining and casual dining. It is fully renovated with brand new centralized air conditioning and heating units, new air ducts, new water heater, newly painted inside of the house and new wood-like vinyl flooring.
